<section class="primary-content">
  <h2 id="akuma">Akuma</h2>

  <p><strong>Kit is only available to club members - <a href="/membership">join us today!</a></strong></p>

  <p>We've chosen <a href="http://www.akumacycling.com/">Akuma Cycling</a> as our manufacturer of choice. They have a great range of items including casual wear and are very competitive on price. They have a really small minimum and a 3 week turnaround once we've signed off the design so we can get kit into your hands really quickly.</p>

  <p>Having received some items already we can assure you the quality is second to none.</p>

  <p>Please feel free to have a look though the full <a href="http://www.akumacycling.com/wp-content/uploads/Akuma-Cycling-2015.pdf">2015 Akuma Cycling brochure</a>, we can order anything from it.</p>

  <h2 id="thekit">The Kit</h2>

  <p>Below are items we've already had Akuma make up for us, these will have a shorter lead time as the design work has already been done.</p>

  <p><em>We don't add anything to the price that Akuma charge us.</em></p>

  <p><em>Prices correct as of 02/03/2016.</em></p>

  <h3 id="ssjersey">S/S Jersey</h3>

  <img src="<%= asset_path('template/SCCJersey.jpg') %>" alt="">

  <p>We have two options on this, we can use the cheaper INIZIO jersey or the slightly better quality and higher priced LEBERG jersey. Both come with a full zip for those glorious summer days where you can do your best <a href="/assets/img/voeckler.jpg">Thomas Voeckler</a> impression.</p>

  <h4 id="inizio">Inizio</h4>

  <blockquote>
    <p>Designed to suit all tiers of rider, the Inizio Jersey is a simple, efficiently cut garment that promotes wicking to keep you cool and comfortable.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <p><strong>Price: £39.60</strong></p>

  <h4 id="leberg">Leberg</h4>

  <blockquote>
    <p>The Leberg Jersey is a multi-panelled lightweight jersey that provides both wicking &amp; ventilation whilst providing extra visibility through reflective piping.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <p><strong>Price: £51.00</strong></p>

  <h3 id="regiabibshorts">Regia Bibshorts</h3>

  <img src="<%= asset_path('template/SCCShorts.jpg') %>" alt="">

  <blockquote>
    <p>The Regia Bib offers full support whilst affording more customisation with the sublimatable panel on the outer thigh. For added comfort the shoulder seam of the bib has been altered to sit at the front of the garment.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <p>There's 3 leg lengths available in this. The regular cut, then the short cut (-4cm in length) and long cut (+4cm in length)</p>

  <p><strong>Price: £64.79</strong></p>

  <h3 id="inbergilet">Inber Gilet</h3>

  <blockquote>
    <p>The Inber Gilet is a great lightweight addition to your kit. With a water-repellent and windproof body and back mesh mid-section for ventilation, it is great for breezy or showery rides.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <p><strong>Price: £84.00</strong></p>

  <h3 id="roubaixbibtights">Roubaix Bibtights</h3>

  <blockquote>
    <p>Our Roubaix Bib is constructed using our water-repellant, fleece backed Thermovel fabric. Thermovel helps keep you warm and dry, perfect for cold climates and winter rides.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <p>Again there are a a few different lengths available on these. </p>

  <p><strong>Price: £72.00</strong></p>

  <h3 id="espesowinterjacket">Espeso Winter Jacket</h3>

  <blockquote>
    <p>The Espeso Winter Jacket is a fully sublimatable, windproof and water-repellent outerlayer. Featuring a Windtex membrane, the garment helps keep you warm without weighing you down.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <p><strong>Price: £90.00</strong></p>

  <h3 id="espesowinterjacket">Arm Warmers, Knee Warmers and Leg Warmers</h3>

  <blockquote>
    <p>All accessories are made in our smooth surfaced Koppenvel fabric. This allows us to sublimate any design you would like onto the garments without compromising on quality.</p>
  </blockquote>

  <p><strong>Price: £19.19 for the Arm and Leg Warmers, £17.99 for the Knee Warmers</strong></p>

  <h2 id="sizing">Sizing</h2>

  <p>Akuma have a <a href="http://www.akumacycling.com/technical-area/sizing-guides/">size guide</a> here. Their sizing is pretty much spot on and better suited to British riders. We can get our hands on sample garments if you're not sure, and you can always ask a member to lend you their kit.</p>

  <h2 id="ordering">Ordering</h2>

  <p>Ordering is easy. Just send us an <a href="mailto:team@sitwell.cc?subject=Kit">email</a> with your requirements and we'll take it from there.</p>
</section>

